<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Enacted and Promulgated by Ministry of National Defense on July 4th, 2001; The Regulations will be put into practice from the date of promulgation.
2.Article 4,6,9 and table of organization were amended and promulgated by Ministry of National Defense on September 14th,2004.
